    "description": "<strong>Bean To Me!</strong><br>Use strange and magical beans to bend the rules and chain together absurd synergies in a wild twist on the ancient game of <i>Mancala</i>! <br>Battle friends and foes alike in the ultimate test of bean-pushing strategy! Gather beans, strike multiple times with Bonus turns, and Steal massive piles of beans when your opponent is distracted!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Weird Beans</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001670/extras/207d76a80a8949d2bb93d7a3338bae38.webp?t=1745534003\" width=32 height=32 /></span><br>Create the perfect arsenal of bizarre beans, each with their own powers. But be careful; anything you bring into a match could end up on the other side of the board and used against you! Unlock them by completing special challenges, and by cracking open a refreshing can of beans every few matches!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle Your Friends</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001670/extras/005ac229879d7b065857513a3454bd74.webp?t=1745534003\" width=32 height=32 /></span><br>Battle your best buds with your best beans - challenge them head-to-head bean battles in both online and local multiplayer!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master The Strategy</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001670/extras/2bd1a0674c31c416c39267e0b934cc0e.webp?t=1745534003\" width=32 height=32 /></span><br>Dig down into one of the world's oldest mind games, and discover the rich strategies within; do you hold off on scoring big on your turn to increase the potential synergies of your beans? Or do you bait your opponent into Stealing a particularly troublesome Bomb Bean?",
